ing the PMTs in liquid xenon using\nthe XENON1T signal readout components including voltage dividers, cables and\nfeedthroughs. The PMTs tested in liquid xenon demonstrated a stable operation\nfor a time period of more than 5 months.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Feb 2015 20:33:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-13"}
