, thus leading to the most comprehensive picture of keV\nsterile neutrino DM production by singlet scalar decays that exists up to now.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Feb 2015 20:52:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Feb 2015 09:10:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2015 13:09:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
