sult for the\nisotope shift is also obtained. Notably, both the quantum and the isotope\neffects for the prism-cage energy difference are small.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Feb 2015 21:41:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-28"}
